{"type":"message","id":"b74ad45f","parentId":"3dce955f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T03:11:34.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Excellent. Here’s the full design-system brief:\n\n**Design System Brief**\n- **App type:** e-commerce app\n- **Style:** premium luxury\n- **Primary color:** black\n- **Target users:** affluent men and women\n- **Scope:** all screens\n\n**Recommended visual direction**\n- **Core palette:** black, ivory, charcoal, soft gold\n- **Mood:** elegant, exclusive, refined, minimal\n- **Typography:** high-contrast luxury serif for headings + clean sans-serif for UI/body\n- **Components:** spacious cards, large product imagery, subtle borders, restrained shadows\n- **Buttons:** bold black primary actions, gold or ivory accents, clean hover states\n- **Layout:** generous whitespace, editorial-style sections, strong visual hierarchy\n- **Imagery:** premium fashion/jewelry/watch-style presentation with cinematic crops\n- **Motion:** subtle fades, smooth hover lift, minimal but polished transitions\n\n**Screens to cover**\n- home\n- category / product listing\n- product detail\n- search\n- wishlist\n- cart\n- checkout\n- profile / account\n- order history\n- authentication\n- brand / collection landing pages\n\nIf you want, I can next turn this into:\n1. a **design-system spec**, or  \n2. a **screen-generation prompt** for Stitch/UI creation."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":2356,"output":310,"cacheRead":17920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775963477120,"responseId":"1775963478940"}}
