{"type":"message","id":"26de37c3","parentId":"1a90f698","timestamp":"2026-04-12T03:12:37.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Perfect — here’s **1 → 2**:\n\n## 1. Design System Spec\n\n**Brand**\n- Premium luxury e-commerce for affluent men and women\n- Tone: exclusive, elegant, minimal, editorial\n\n**Color System**\n- Primary: **Black**\n- Secondary: **Soft Gold**\n- Background: **Ivory / Warm White**\n- Surface: **Charcoal / Deep Gray**\n- Text:\n  - Primary text: near-black\n  - Secondary text: muted gray\n  - Inverse text: ivory/white\n\n**Suggested palette**\n- Black: `#0B0B0C`\n- Charcoal: `#1A1A1D`\n- Ivory: `#F6F1E8`\n- Warm White: `#FAF8F4`\n- Soft Gold: `#C6A972`\n- Muted Gray: `#8C8C8F`\n\n**Typography**\n- Headings: elegant serif style\n- Body/UI: clean modern sans-serif\n- Feel: fashion-house / luxury boutique\n- Use large, spacious headlines and restrained body text\n\n**Spacing & Layout**\n- Generous whitespace\n- Large image-first sections\n- Premium editorial grid\n- Clear hierarchy with fewer but stronger elements\n\n**Shape**\n- Slightly rounded or nearly-square corners\n- Avoid playful curves\n- Refined, sharp, confident geometry\n\n**Components**\n- Buttons: black primary, gold accent, ivory secondary\n- Cards: minimal borders, subtle elevation\n- Inputs: clean lines, generous padding, premium focus states\n- Navigation: simple top nav, strong typography, elegant spacing\n- Product tiles: big imagery, minimal text, price and CTA balanced carefully\n\n**Imagery**\n- Large luxurious photography\n- Dark, moody, high-contrast visuals\n- Focus on craftsmanship, material, exclusivity\n\n**Motion**\n- Soft fade-ins\n- Gentle hover lift\n- Smooth premium transitions\n- No flashy animation\n\n---\n\n## 2. Screen-Generation Prompt\n\nUse this prompt for UI/screen generation:\n\n**Prompt:**\n\n> Create a full premium luxury e-commerce app design system and screen set for all major screens. The brand should target affluent men and women and feel elegant, exclusive, timeless, and minimal. Use black as the primary color, supported by soft gold, ivory, warm white, and charcoal neutrals.  \n>  \n> The visual language should feel like a high-end fashion or luxury goods brand, with large editorial-style product imagery, generous whitespace, refined typography, and polished but subtle interactions. Use elegant serif typography for headings and a clean sans-serif for body and interface text.  \n>  \n> Design all key screens, including home, collection/category listing, product detail, search, wishlist, cart, checkout, authentication, profile/account, and order history.  \n>  \n> Components should include premium buttons, cards, navigation, filters, inputs, product tiles, badges, and checkout sections. Favor minimal layouts, strong visual hierarchy, clean alignment, subtle borders, and restrained shadows.  \n>  \n> The overall result should look cinematic, high-end, and conversion-focused, with a luxury editorial aesthetic suitable for rich male and female shoppers.\n\nIf you want, I can also make this into:\n- a **shorter Stitch-ready prompt**, or\n- a **more detailed component-by-component prompt**."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":2552,"output":745,"cacheRead":18176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775963519174,"responseId":"1775963520926"}}
