{"type":"message","id":"94d8650e","parentId":"87983064","timestamp":"2026-04-12T03:25:31.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Absolutely — here’s a **detailed component-by-component prompt** you can use:\n\n---\n\n**Detailed UI Generation Prompt**\n\nCreate a **premium luxury e-commerce app** for **affluent men and women**. The design should feel **exclusive, elegant, timeless, minimal, editorial, and high-end**. The brand aesthetic should resemble a luxury fashion house, premium watch brand, or elite lifestyle retailer.\n\n## Global Design Direction\n- Use **black** as the primary brand color.\n- Support it with **soft gold, ivory, warm white, and charcoal** neutrals.\n- Keep the interface **clean, spacious, and image-led**.\n- Use **elegant serif typography for headings** and **modern sans-serif typography for body text, labels, and controls**.\n- Prioritize **large premium product imagery**, **generous whitespace**, **subtle borders**, **refined alignment**, and **strong visual hierarchy**.\n- Motion should be **soft and luxurious**, with restrained hover states, smooth transitions, and minimal animation.\n- Avoid anything playful, noisy, overly colorful, cartoonish, or cluttered.\n\n## Color Palette\nUse a polished luxury palette like:\n- Primary black: `#0B0B0C`\n- Deep charcoal: `#1A1A1D`\n- Soft gold: `#C6A972`\n- Ivory: `#F6F1E8`\n- Warm white: `#FAF8F4`\n- Muted gray: `#8C8C8F`\n\n## Typography\n- Headings: elegant serif, high contrast, fashion-editorial style\n- Subheadings: refined serif or premium sans-serif\n- Body/UI text: clean sans-serif, modern and highly legible\n- Use large hero typography, restrained supporting text, and premium spacing between lines and sections\n\n## Layout Principles\n- Editorial composition\n- Strong use of negative space\n- Symmetrical and asymmetrical luxury layouts where appropriate\n- Large full-width banners and immersive photography\n- Clear hierarchy with fewer, stronger elements\n- Product discovery should feel curated, not crowded\n\n---\n\n# Component-by-Component Requirements\n\n## 1. Header / Navigation\nDesign a luxury top navigation bar with:\n- premium wordmark/logo placement\n- minimal menu items\n- search icon or elegant search entry\n- wishlist icon\n- account/profile icon\n- cart icon\n- optional announcement bar for exclusive promotions\n- sticky behavior with refined transition on scroll\n- desktop and mobile responsive behavior\n\nStyle notes:\n- black / ivory theme\n- thin separators or subtle borders\n- elegant spacing and typography\n- no bulky nav styling\n\n## 2. Hero Section\nDesign a cinematic homepage hero section with:\n- oversized luxury brand imagery\n- bold editorial headline\n- refined supporting copy\n- premium CTA buttons like “Shop Collection” or “Discover Now”\n- optional secondary CTA\n- possible split layout or full-bleed image layout\n\nStyle notes:\n- dramatic, high-end, fashion campaign aesthetic\n- minimal text with strong confidence\n- immersive presentation\n\n## 3. Category / Collection Cards\nDesign collection modules for categories like:\n- men\n- women\n- accessories\n- new arrivals\n- limited edition\n\nRequirements:\n- strong imagery-first layout\n- clean labels and short premium titles\n- hover state with subtle lift or image zoom\n- possible gold accent or refined overlay\n- editorial-style grid\n\n## 4. Product Listing / Catalog Grid\nDesign a product listing page with:\n- premium product card grid\n- elegant filters sidebar or filter drawer\n- sort dropdown\n- collection title and intro text\n- breadcrumbs\n- item count\n- pagination or infinite loading\n\nEach product card should include:\n- large product image\n- product name\n- short category/descriptor\n- price\n- optional badge like “Exclusive”, “New”, “Limited”\n- hover actions such as quick view or wishlist\n\nStyle notes:\n- uncluttered cards\n- plenty of breathing space\n- premium fashion retail feel\n\n## 5. Filters and Sort Controls\nDesign luxury filter UI for:\n- category\n- size\n- color\n- material\n- brand\n- price range\n- availability\n- collection\n\nRequirements:\n- elegant checkboxes, toggles, pills, or accordion filters\n- clean dropdown for sorting\n- premium mobile filter drawer\n- refined active states and hover states\n- no overly technical or enterprise-looking controls\n\n## 6. Product Detail Page\nDesign a premium product detail screen with:\n- large image gallery\n- zoomable product photos\n- product title\n- short luxury descriptor\n- price\n- size or variant selector\n- color selector\n- quantity selector\n- add to cart button\n- wishlist button\n- shipping / returns summary\n- accordions for details, materials, care, sizing\n- related products section\n- optional craftsmanship/storytelling section\n\nStyle notes:\n- immersive image-first presentation\n- premium CTA hierarchy\n- elegant spacing and typography\n- trust and exclusivity without visual noise\n\n## 7. Buttons\nCreate a premium button system including:\n- primary button\n- secondary button\n- ghost button\n- text button\n- icon button\n\nStyle direction:\n- black primary button with ivory or white text\n- gold accent version where suitable\n- elegant hover transitions\n- slightly rounded or crisp corners\n- strong padding and refined proportions\n- disabled, hover, pressed, and focus states\n\n## 8. Form Inputs\nDesign refined luxury form controls for:\n- text input\n- email input\n- password input\n- search field\n- phone field\n- select dropdown\n- date input if needed\n- textarea\n\nStyle notes:\n- generous padding\n- subtle borders\n- elegant focus glow or gold-accent focus ring\n- high readability\n- polished validation states\n- no harsh enterprise feel\n\n## 9. Search Experience\nDesign a premium search experience with:\n- top search overlay or dedicated search screen\n- trending searches\n- suggested collections\n- recent searches\n- product suggestions with thumbnails\n- empty state and no-result state\n\nStyle notes:\n- fast, minimal, elegant\n- luxury retail discovery feel\n- visually rich but uncluttered\n\n## 10. Wishlist\nDesign a wishlist screen with:\n- saved product grid\n- ability to move to cart\n- remove item action\n- empty state with premium recommendation CTA\n- elegant pricing and product previews\n\nStyle notes:\n- curated luxury closet feel\n- clean card layouts\n- editorial spacing\n\n## 11. Cart\nDesign a luxury shopping cart with:\n- product summary cards\n- quantity controls\n- remove action\n- price breakdown\n- shipping estimate\n- promo code input\n- recommendation section\n- CTA to checkout\n\nStyle notes:\n- premium checkout funnel feel\n- clear totals\n- elegant spacing\n- high trust presentation\n\n## 12. Checkout\nDesign a premium checkout experience with:\n- shipping information section\n- billing details\n- payment method selector\n- order summary\n- promo code\n- shipping method options\n- secure payment indicators\n- final place-order CTA\n\nStyle notes:\n- minimal friction\n- high trust\n- luxury but conversion-focused\n- premium form layout\n- refined section grouping\n\n## 13. Authentication\nDesign elegant auth screens for:\n- sign in\n- sign up\n- forgot password\n- OTP / verification if needed\n\nStyle notes:\n- minimal and sophisticated\n- luxury background imagery or subtle texture optional\n- premium typography\n- frictionless but exclusive feel\n\n## 14. Profile / Account Dashboard\nDesign an account area with:\n- personal details\n- saved addresses\n- payment methods\n- order history\n- wishlist shortcut\n- logout\n- settings\n\nStyle notes:\n- polished dashboard\n- clear navigation\n- feels like a premium membership area\n\n## 15. Order History / Order Detail\nDesign order history and order detail screens with:\n- order cards or table-like premium list\n- status badges\n- order number\n- date\n- total\n- item preview\n- reorder / track package actions\n- detailed order breakdown\n\nStyle notes:\n- high clarity\n- refined utility\n- not overly dense\n\n## 16. Promotional Banners / Editorial Sections\nDesign supporting modules such as:\n- featured collections\n- seasonal campaigns\n- limited edition drops\n- craftsmanship/storytelling panels\n- designer spotlight\n- premium membership or concierge services\n\nStyle notes:\n- luxury magazine aesthetic\n- strong photography\n- elegant typography and composition\n\n## 17. Footer\nDesign a premium footer with:\n- logo/brand mark\n- navigation links\n- customer care\n- returns/shipping info\n- social links\n- newsletter signup\n- legal links\n\nStyle notes:\n- understated\n- elegant\n- dark, refined, well-spaced\n\n## 18. Cards and Tiles\nCreate a reusable luxury card system for:\n- products\n- collections\n- recommendations\n- editorials\n- order summaries\n\nStyle notes:\n- subtle border or shadow\n- image-led\n- premium padding\n- refined hierarchy\n\n## 19. Badges and Labels\nDesign tasteful badges such as:\n- new\n- exclusive\n- limited\n- best seller\n- sold out\n\nStyle notes:\n- understated and premium\n- avoid bright retail-sale aesthetics\n- gold, black, ivory, and muted grayscale emphasis\n\n## 20. Empty States\nDesign empty states for:\n- wishlist empty\n- cart empty\n- no search results\n- no orders yet\n\nStyle notes:\n- elegant copy\n- premium illustrations or minimalist iconography\n- clear high-end CTAs\n\n## 21. Mobile Experience\nEnsure the mobile version preserves luxury feel with:\n- clean bottom or top navigation behavior\n- immersive mobile hero sections\n- premium filter drawer\n- elegant checkout flow\n- image-first product browsing\n- touch-friendly but minimal controls\n\n## 22. Microinteractions\nUse subtle premium motion for:\n- button hover\n- image zoom on hover\n- card lift\n- menu reveal\n- modal transitions\n- drawer transitions\n- loading states\n\nMotion style:\n- smooth\n- restrained\n- expensive feeling\n- never flashy or gamified\n\n---\n\n# Screen Set to Generate\nGenerate all major screens:\n1. Home\n2. Collection / Category Listing\n3. Search\n4. Product Detail\n5. Wishlist\n6. Cart\n7. Checkout\n8. Sign In\n9. Sign Up\n10. Forgot Password\n11. Profile / Account\n12. Order History\n13. Order Detail\n14. Featured Collection Landing Page\n15. Editorial Campaign / Brand Story Page\n\n---\n\n# Final Quality Target\nThe result should feel like:\n- luxury fashion commerce\n- premium editorial design\n- cinematic product presentation\n- elegant, exclusive, and trustworthy\n- modern but timeless\n- optimized for affluent male and female shoppers\n\nAvoid:\n- generic marketplace look\n- bright discount-store aesthetics\n- cluttered UI\n- childish visuals\n- overly technical dashboard styling\n\n---\n\nIf you want, I can next compress this into a **short Stitch-ready production prompt**."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":3039,"output":2305,"cacheRead":18560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23904,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775964218007,"responseId":"1775964220235"}}
