{"type":"message","id":"0cb37c46","parentId":"09bba039","timestamp":"2026-04-12T03:34:53.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The prompt-optimizer agent was spawned successfully. Now I need to wait for it to complete and then hand off to the design agents. I'll report the pipeline status to the user.","thinkingSignature":"43e3e8230ac61576fbea0b64a0f3c4d9c84d752c569bc56823b26fe0c99ac37a"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Pipeline: Active**\n\n- **Step 1:** `prompt-optimizer` spawned — optimizing the brief now\n- **Step 2 (pending):** → `ui-ux-pro-max` for UX direction\n- **Step 3 (pending):** → `ui-design-system` for design tokens\n- **Step 4 (pending):** → `stitch-design` for Stitch generation\n\nAwaiting `prompt-optimizer` completion. I’ll automatically fan out to the next agents once the brief is ready."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":255,"output":147,"cacheRead":29749,"cacheWrite":999,"totalTokens":31150,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775964888392,"responseId":"062a45d9540eff00cc6bbe41d04eef83"}}
