{"type":"message","id":"7838ba76","parentId":"7d7d7249","timestamp":"2026-04-12T03:48:52.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The pipeline is working. I can see:\n\n1. `prompt-optimizer` completed successfully (after the earlier failure) - it produced a full optimization of the brief\n2. `ui-ux-pro-max` completed successfully - it wrote HANDOVER.md and dispatched to ui-design-system and stitch-design\n3. `ui-design-system` is currently running (session `agent:ui-design-system:main`) - it received the handoff and is working on it\n4. `stitch-design` session exists but has no messages yet\n\nThe HANDOVER.md is excellent - very detailed UX direction document. \n\nNow I'm waiting for ui-design-system and stitch-design to complete their work, and I should give the user a status update on where things stand.","thinkingSignature":"473ab19eed1a13dc8869ef7f537a9c29bae04c5df01b0e36971b3d8ff2bfa705"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🌐 **Pipeline: Active — Good Progress**\n\nBoth agents completed their passes:\n\n| Step | Agent | Status |\n|------|-------|--------|\n| 1 | `prompt-optimizer` | ✅ Done — full brief optimized |\n| 2 | `ui-ux-pro-max` | ✅ Done — UX direction + HANDOVER.md written |\n| 3 | `ui-design-system` | 🔄 Running — received HANDOVER, building design tokens |\n| 4 | `stitch-design` | ⏳ Standby — waiting for design tokens to hand off |\n\n**HANDOVER.md** produced:\n- 5 user flows (Browse → Purchase → Track)\n- Mobile-first IA and nav hierarchy\n- 12 priority components standardized\n- Luxury motion guidelines (160–380ms, ease-out, restrained)\n- 10 luxury UX principles (restraint, storytelling, confidence, exclusivity)\n- Screen-by-screen intent for all 15 screens\n\n`ui-design-system` is currently working on converting this into semantic color tokens, type scale, spacing system, and component specs. Once it completes, `stitch-design` will generate the actual Stitch screens."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":11318,"output":400,"cacheRead":35990,"cacheWrite":659,"totalTokens":48367,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775965719289,"responseId":"062a491844e04f0f6a06dd3440b2ecb4"}}
