{"type":"message","id":"f2907da2","parentId":"3b40519f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T03:57:55.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me report the current status:\n\n1. `prompt-optimizer` — ✅ Done\n2. `ui-ux-pro-max` — ✅ Done  \n3. `ui-design-system` — ❌ Failed (ran but failed - model timeout/error)\n4. `stitch-design` — 🔄 Running (received the brief, working on Stitch generation)\n\nSo the chain is:\n- ui-design-system FAILED — this means stitch-design may not have the proper design tokens\n- stitch-design is still running\n\nI need to report this clearly to the user and take action. Since ui-design-system failed, stitch-design might be working from the raw HANDOVER.md rather than the refined design tokens.","thinkingSignature":"300158e81a4ca0d4554674017f6b2c048eff09c7463059db7d1729d7bd660ba4"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 📊 **Pipeline Status — cập nhật lúc 10:57 UTC+7**\n\n| Bước | Agent | Trạng thái |\n|------|-------|-----------|\n| 1 | `prompt-optimizer` | ✅ Hoàn thành |\n| 2 | `ui-ux-pro-max` | ✅ Hoàn thành — UX direction + HANDOVER.md |\n| 3 | `ui-design-system` | ❌ Thất bại — model timeout |\n| 4 | `stitch-design` | 🔄 **Đang chạy** — nhận brief trực tiếp từ ui-ux-pro-max |\n\n**Vấn đề:** `ui-design-system` bị timeout nên bước design tokens bị bỏ qua. `stitch-design` đang làm việc với HANDOVER.md thô.\n\nMình cần restart `ui-design-system` sau để bổ sung design tokens. Muốn restart ngay bây giờ không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":6092,"output":387,"cacheRead":51246,"cacheWrite":466,"totalTokens":58191,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775966264113,"responseId":"062a4b3960321d54232c8470fa217639"}}
