{"type":"message","id":"d5235d7c","parentId":"133729d1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:01:27.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The list_screens call returned permission denied. The Stitch MCP might not have access to read our project. Let me try generating screens with the design system reference and then apply the design system.\n\nActually, I think the approach should be:\n1. Generate screens in our project using the design system reference design (\"Aethelgard Noir\") as the design direction\n2. Then apply the design system to those screens\n\nBut since I can't list screens, let me just try to generate screens with a prompt that incorporates the \"Aethelgard Noir\" / \"The Cinematic Editorial\" design system details, and then apply the design system.\n\nActually, looking at the stitch tools more carefully:\n\n\n- `stitch__generate_screen_from_text` - generates screens from text prompt\n- `stitch__apply_design_system` - applies a design system to existing screens\n- `stitch__create_design_system` - creates a new design system\n\nThe key insight is that I can create the design system in our project first, then generate screens with it. But the design system already exists in the reference project. Maybe I should create a new design system in our project based on the \"Aethelgard Noir\" design system details, then generate screens with it. Or I could try `stitch__generate_screen_from_text` with a prompt that includes the design system specifications and applies them during generation. The `stitch__apply_design_system` tool applies a design system to screens after they're created, so I might need to generate screens first and then apply the design system as a separate step. Since the previous generation attempts timed out, I should simplify the prompt and try again with retry logic. My plan is to generate screens in our project using the design system specifications as guidance, then apply the design system to the generated screens. But first I need to figure out how to create the design system in our project since `stitch__create_design_system` requires a design system object and I don't have the full reference project structure. Let me just generate screens with the design specifications included in the prompt and see if that works.\n\nActually, I realize the design system is already defined in the reference project, so I should try to create a design system in our project using those same specifications. Let me check if there's an easier path through the Stitch tools or if I need to construct the design system object from the reference details.","thinkingSignature":"e4ee451d6c365ce36e3367fb3703b9d2d2c461be8731925d5a50cd468c8bc06b"},{"type":"text","text":"Can't read our project screens. Let me create the design system directly in our project, then generate screens with it.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_41w9xglvqxhb_1","name":"stitch__create_design_system","arguments":{"designSystem":"{\"displayName\": \"Aethelgard Noir\", \"theme\": {\"colorMode\": \"LIGHT\", \"font\": \"NOTO_SERIF\", \"customColor\": \"#000000\", \"headlineFont\": \"NOTO_SERIF\", \"bodyFont\": \"MANROPE\", \"labelFont\": \"MANROPE\", \"namedColors\": {\"background\": \"#f9f9f9\", \"error\": \"#9e3f4e\", \"error_container\": \"#ff8b9a\", \"error_dim\": \"#4f0116\", \"inverse_on_surface\": \"#9c9d9d\", \"inverse_primary\": \"#ffffff\", \"inverse_surface\": \"#0c0f0f\", \"on_background\": \"#2d3435\", \"on_error\": \"#fff7f7\", \"on_error_container\": \"#782232\", \"on_primary\": \"#f8f8f8\", \"on_primary_container\": \"#525252\", \"on_primary_fixed\": \"#3f3f3f\", \"on_primary_fixed_variant\": \"#5b5b5b\", \"on_secondary\": \"#fff8ef\", \"on_secondary_container\": \"#644f00\", \"on_secondary_fixed\": \"#4e3d00\", \"on_secondary_fixed_variant\": \"#705900\", \"on_surface\": \"#2d3435\", \"on_surface_variant\": \"#5a6061\", \"on_tertiary\": \"#fbf8f8\", \"on_tertiary_container\": \"#5c5b5b\", \"on_tertiary_fixed\": \"#4a4949\", \"on_tertiary_fixed_variant\": \"#676666\", \"outline\": \"#757c7d\", \"outline_variant\": \"#adb3b4\", \"primary\": \"#5e5e5e\", \"primary_container\": \"#e2e2e2\", \"primary_dim\": \"#525252\", \"primary_fixed\": \"#e2e2e2\", \"primary_fixed_dim\": \"#d4d4d4\", \"secondary\": \"#745c00\", \"secondary_container\": \"#ffe088\", \"secondary_dim\": \"#665100\", \"secondary_fixed\": \"#ffe088\", \"secondary_fixed_dim\": \"#f8d056\", \"surface\": \"#f9f9f9\", \"surface_bright\": \"#f9f9f9\", \"surface_container\": \"#ebeeef\", \"surface_container_high\": \"#e4e9ea\", \"surface_container_highest\": \"#dde4e5\", \"surface_container_low\": \"#f2f4f4\", \"surface_container_lowest\": \"#ffffff\", \"surface_dim\": \"#d3dbdd\", \"surface_tint\": \"#5e5e5e\", \"surface_variant\": \"#dde4e5\", \"tertiary\": \"#5f5f5f\", \"tertiary_container\": \"#f6f3f2\", \"tertiary_dim\": \"#535353\", \"tertiary_fixed\": \"#f6f3f2\", \"tertiary_fixed_dim\": \"#e7e5e4\"}, \"designMd\": \"# Design System: Aethelgard Noir\\n\\n## Overview: The Digital Curator\\nA cinematic editorial luxury e-commerce system. No clutter, no borders, no compromise.\\n\\n## Colors\\n- Primary: #5e5e5e (charcoal) — UI logic\\n- Secondary: #745c00 / #D4AF37 (soft gold) — moments of truth, premium CTA\\n- Surface: #f9f9f9 (ivory) — warm base\\n- On Surface: #2d3435 — text\\n\\n## Typography\\n- Headlines: NOTO_SERIF — editorial, tight tracking (-2%)\\n- Body/UI: MANROPE — geometric clarity\\n\\n## Key Rules\\n- NO 1px borders — use background color shifts instead\\n- 0px border radius — strict square, luxury is sharp\\n- Glassmorphism for floating elements (80% opacity + 20px blur)\\n- Ambient shadows: box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(45,52,53,0.04)\\n- Ghost borders at 15% opacity max\\n- 400ms ease-in-out for all interactions\\n- Asymmetrical hero margins\\n- No icon-only buttons — always label + icon\\n- Soft gold (#D4AF37) for promotions, never sale red\", \"colorVariant\": \"NEUTRAL\", \"overridePrimaryColor\": \"#000000\", \"overrideSecondaryColor\": \"#D4AF37\", \"overrideTertiaryColor\": \"#333333\", \"overrideNeutralColor\": \"#FDFDFD\", \"spacingScale\": 3}}","projectId":"12108154905534221530"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":88,"output":1548,"cacheRead":71417,"cacheWrite":2973,"totalTokens":76026,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775973662222,"responseId":"062a681f0e6aa4ecdb73840c88531ae1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3bab45bf","parentId":"d5235d7c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:01:27.478Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_41w9xglvqxhb_1","toolName":"stitch__create_design_system","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Validation failed for tool \"stitch__create_design_system\":\n  - designSystem: must be object\n\nReceived arguments:\n{\n  \"designSystem\": \"{\\\"displayName\\\": \\\"Aethelgard Noir\\\", \\\"theme\\\": {\\\"colorMode\\\": \\\"LIGHT\\\", \\\"font\\\": \\\"NOTO_SERIF\\\", \\\"customColor\\\": \\\"#000000\\\", \\\"headlineFont\\\": \\\"NOTO_SERIF\\\", \\\"bodyFont\\\": \\\"MANROPE\\\", \\\"labelFont\\\": \\\"MANROPE\\\", \\\"namedColors\\\": {\\\"background\\\": \\\"#f9f9f9\\\", \\\"error\\\": \\\"#9e3f4e\\\", \\\"error_container\\\": \\\"#ff8b9a\\\", \\\"error_dim\\\": \\\"#4f0116\\\", \\\"inverse_on_surface\\\": \\\"#9c9d9d\\\", \\\"inverse_primary\\\": \\\"#ffffff\\\", \\\"inverse_surface\\\": \\\"#0c0f0f\\\", \\\"on_background\\\": \\\"#2d3435\\\", \\\"on_error\\\": \\\"#fff7f7\\\", \\\"on_error_container\\\": \\\"#782232\\\", \\\"on_primary\\\": \\\"#f8f8f8\\\", \\\"on_primary_container\\\": \\\"#525252\\\", \\\"on_primary_fixed\\\": \\\"#3f3f3f\\\", \\\"on_primary_fixed_variant\\\": \\\"#5b5b5b\\\", \\\"on_secondary\\\": \\\"#fff8ef\\\", \\\"on_secondary_container\\\": \\\"#644f00\\\", \\\"on_secondary_fixed\\\": \\\"#4e3d00\\\", \\\"on_secondary_fixed_variant\\\": \\\"#705900\\\", \\\"on_surface\\\": \\\"#2d3435\\\", \\\"on_surface_variant\\\": \\\"#5a6061\\\", \\\"on_tertiary\\\": \\\"#fbf8f8\\\", \\\"on_tertiary_container\\\": \\\"#5c5b5b\\\", \\\"on_tertiary_fixed\\\": \\\"#4a4949\\\", \\\"on_tertiary_fixed_variant\\\": \\\"#676666\\\", \\\"outline\\\": \\\"#757c7d\\\", \\\"outline_variant\\\": \\\"#adb3b4\\\", \\\"primary\\\": \\\"#5e5e5e\\\", \\\"primary_container\\\": \\\"#e2e2e2\\\", \\\"primary_dim\\\": \\\"#525252\\\", \\\"primary_fixed\\\": \\\"#e2e2e2\\\", \\\"primary_fixed_dim\\\": \\\"#d4d4d4\\\", \\\"se