{"type":"message","id":"d4b41263","parentId":"abb6126f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:02:12.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The design system asset `40e982ef8dfb4af2ab0af498ef8cfff6` is not accessible from our project (it's in the reference project `13261989784115652519`). Design systems are scoped to their own project.\n\nSo the correct approach is:\n1. First, generate screens in our project `12108154905534221530` using the \"Aethelgard Noir\" design direction in the prompt\n2. Then the screens will be created in our project\n3. After that, we can try to apply a design system\n\nOR alternatively:\n1. Create a design system in our project `12108154905534221530` first\n\n\n2. Then generate screens with it\n\nLet me focus on getting screens generated first with the \"Aethelgard Noir\" design embedded in the prompt, then tackle applying the design system afterward. I'll update the stitch-design subagent to use the design system details from \"Aethelgard Noir\" directly in the generation prompt.","thinkingSignature":"0513b6606ad757530f50fe83623e580e1799e0e526f2cbca20ea9d936fc0232d"},{"type":"text","text":"Design system is scoped to its own project — can't apply cross-project. Best path: generate screens with \"Aethelgard Noir\" design specs in the prompt, then apply. Updating the running `stitch-design` agent.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9lsukk22ufe1_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:stitch-design:subagent:8782b01c-8fe2-450b-a8aa-a95d0cb3924e","agentId":"stitch-design","message":"CRITICAL UPDATE from Orbis: The user has selected a reference design from this project: https://stitch.withgoogle.com/projects/13261989784115652519 — design system called \"Aethelgard Noir\" / \"The Cinematic Editorial\". Use these exact design specs for all screen generation going forward:\n\nDESIGN SYSTEM: \"Aethelgard Noir\"\n- Creative North Star: The Digital Curator — cinematic editorial, not cluttered e-commerce\n- Primary color: #5e5e5e (charcoal) — NOT black\n- Secondary/Accent: #D4AF37 / #745c00 (soft gold) — moments of truth, premium CTAs\n- Surface: #f9f9f9 (warm ivory) — never clinical white\n- On-surface text: #2d3435\n- Typography: NOTO_SERIF for headlines (editorial, tight tracking), MANROPE for body/UI\n- NO 1px borders — use background color shifts (surface-container tiers) instead\n- 0px border radius — STRICT SQUARE, luxury is sharp and intentional\n- Glassmorphism: surface colors at 80% opacity + 20px backdrop blur for floating elements\n- Ambient shadow: box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(45,52,53,0.04)\n- Ghost borders at 15% opacity max — NEVER solid opaque borders\n- All interactions: minimum 400ms with ease-in-out curve\n- Asymmetrical hero margins (e.g., 10% left, 15% right)\n- NO icon-only buttons — always label + icon together\n- Soft gold for promotions and premium moments — NEVER sale red\n- No divider lines — use spacing (24px/32px gaps) instead\n- Image hover: subtle 0.5s scale-up \"lens zoom\"\n\nSCREENS TO GENERATE (15 total, MOBILE):\n1. Home — cinematic hero, curated categories, editorial sections\n2. Collection/Category Listing — editorial product grid, minimal filters\n3. Search — premium zero-state, predictive, curated suggestions\n4. Product Detail — gallery-first, luxury product storytelling\n5. Wishlist — curated personal closet feel\n6. Cart — premium review, clear totals\n7. Checkout — calm progression, one action per step\n8. Sign In — minimal, elegant, trustworthy\n9. Sign Up — same tone as Sign In\n10. Forgot Password — minimal, refined\n11. Profile/Account — service-oriented dashboard\n12. Order History — clean list with status\n13. Order Detail — structured breakdown\n14. Featured Collection Landing — branded chapter page\n15. Editorial Campaign Page — immersive storytelling with commerce entry points\n\nGenerate screens one at a time. If stitch__generate_screen_from_text times out, wait 20s then retry (max 3 attempts per screen). Use modelId: GEMINI_3_FLASH for generation. Report final screen count when complete.","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":88,"output":964,"cacheRead":77086,"cacheWrite":2555,"totalTokens":80693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775973716313,"responseId":"062a6855f02d2517316ca1583c29ebc9"}}
