{"type":"message","id":"5f3972d5","parentId":"9edb6e8c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:02:55.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sessions_send timed out - the stitch-design subagent is still running but didn't respond to the message in 30 seconds. Let me try a different approach - I'll update the running agent's task by sending it a message, but the session might be in the middle of processing.\n\nActually, the timeout means the agent didn't respond in 30 seconds. But it might still be running. Let me try sending the message again, or alternatively, spawn a new stitch-design agent with the updated design specs.\n\nActually, let me just spawn a new stitch-design agent specifically to generate screens with the \"Aethelgard Noir\" design specs. The running one might be using the old specs.","thinkingSignature":"06f57d913ba45c48e03a6678e788539f4dd9af8a32cb1011e5dfb51f396dc8cf"},{"type":"text","text":"Agent didn't respond to message in time. Spawning a fresh agent with the correct \"Aethelgard Noir\" design specs.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hgsg177p65f9_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Generate all 15 mobile screens for a luxury e-commerce app using the \"Aethelgard Noir\" design system (The Digital Curator). Project: projects/12108154905534221530. Design specs MUST be followed exactly: Primary: #5e5e5e charcoal, Secondary/Accent: #D4AF37 soft gold, Surface: #f9f9f9 ivory, Text: #2d3435. Typography: NOTO_SERIF headlines + MANROPE body. Rules: NO 1px borders (use color shifts), 0px border radius (strict square), glassmorphism floating elements (80% opacity + 20px blur), ambient shadow (0 20px 50px rgba(45,52,53,0.04)), ghost borders at 15% opacity, 400ms ease-in-out interactions, no icon-only buttons, soft gold for promotions only, no divider lines (use spacing). Screens (MOBILE, one at a time): 1) Home, 2) Collection Listing, 3) Search, 4) Product Detail, 5) Wishlist, 6) Cart, 7) Checkout, 8) Sign I