{"type":"message","id":"d4e68e62","parentId":"365928fb","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:07:38.524Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is explaining that the Stitch MCP has a ~40 second timeout in OpenClaw, but Stitch generation takes longer than that. So I need to configure the subagent to handle this: instead of waiting for the Stitch call to complete (which times out), the agent should call Stitch and accept the timeout as expected, then poll/check the result later.\n\nThis is a key architectural insight: the Stitch MCP tool call itself will timeout at ~40s, but the generation continues in the background. The agent needs to:\n1. Call stitch__generate_screen_from_text\n2. Accept the timeout error as normal\n3. Wait/pause for the generation to complete (Stitch continues in background)\n\n\n4. Then verify the output with stitch__list_screens or stitch__get_screen once it's ready\n\nThe real pattern here is fire-and-forget: initiate the generation, handle the expected timeout gracefully, and check back later to see if the work completed. For the next agent, I should frame this as an async operation where the timeout is just a signal to wait rather than a failure.\n\nThe challenge is that Stitch doesn't have a direct callback mechanism, so I'll need to add a delay between the generation call and the verification step to give Stitch time to finish its work in the background.","thinkingSignature":"79293c5d6ae0914c71384d7fefbeec01ab50cedf34fc112381e568837c0982ff"},{"type":"text","text":"Rõ rồi — Stitch MCP timeout ~40s nhưng generation chạy lâu hơn. Pattern đúng: **fire-and-forget** — gọi Stitch, chấp nhận timeout, sau đó poll/check kết quả.\n\nUpdating agent instruction ngay.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_36jeibb2k5he_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:stitch-design:subagent:6a827a6e-363b-4d15-adb5-c31a0113be03","agentId":"stitch-design","message":"CRITICAL: Stitch MCP has a ~40 second timeout. Stitch generation takes longer. The correct pattern is:\n\n1. Call stitch__generate_screen_from_text\n2. If it returns timeout error → this is EXPECTED, not a failure\n3. Wait 45-60 seconds (use exec sleep or wait in code)\n4. Call stitch__list_screens to check if the screen was created\n5. If no screen → retry generation call (fire-and-forget again)\n6. If screen exists → move to next screen\n\nDO NOT abort on Stitch timeout. Treat it as async completion. Poll results after waiting.\n\nWORKFLOW per screen:\n1. stitch__generate_screen_from_text\n2. EXPECT timeout → wait 50s\n3. stitch__list_screens → check if screen was created\n4. If yes → next screen\n5. If no → go back to step 1 (max 3 total attempts per screen)\n\nStart from screen 1 now with this pattern.","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":618,"cacheRead":80346,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80964,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775974035020,"responseId":"062a6994918a169ba0ab82a10b2bb226"}}
{"type":"message","id":"498e5a91","parentId":"d4e68e62","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:08:09.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_36jeibb2k5he_1","toolName":"sessions_send","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"runId\": \"0a26aba6-fa1a-4c6b-824c-d134ddd7e3ab\",\n  \"status\": \"timeout\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:stitch-design:subagent:6a827a6e-363b-4d15-adb5-c31a0113be03\"\n}"}],"details":{"runId":"0a26aba6-fa1a-4c6b-824c-d134ddd7e3ab","status":"timeout","sessionKey":"agent:stitch-design:subagent:6a827a6e-363b-4d15-adb5-c31a0113be03"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775974089573}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad9b3a32","parentId":"498e5a91","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:08:22.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sessions_send timed out again. This means the agent is either busy running Stitch or not responding. Let me spawn a new agent with the corrected instructions.\n\nActually, I should just spawn a new agent with the corrected fire-and-forget + poll pattern instructions baked into the task.","thinkingSignature":"41d001a3b0b5ae94ae83e76ed3951caaff17154101f8073541128eeec6edb2ee"},{"type":"text","text":"Agent not responding to message. Spawning fresh agent with the corrected timeout-handling pattern baked in.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xduu9gyzypid_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Generate 15 mobile screens for a luxury e-commerce app using the \"Aethelgard Noir\" design system. Project: projects/12108154905534221530.\n\n## CRITICAL TIMEOUT HANDLING\nStitch MCP has a ~40 second timeout. Stitch generation takes longer. The correct pattern is FIRE-AND-FORGET + POLL:\n1. Call stitch__generate_screen_from_text\n2. If it returns timeout error → EXPECTED, not a failure\n3. Wait 50 seconds (exec sleep 50)\n4. Call stitch__list_screens to check if the screen was created\n5. If screen exists → move to next screen\n6. If no screen → retry from step 1 (max 3 attempts per screen)\nDO NOT abort on Stitch timeout. Treat it as async completion.\n\n## Design System: \"Aethelgard Noir\" (follow exactly)\n- Primary: #5e5e5e charcoal\n- Secondary/Accent: #D4AF37 soft gold\n- Surface: #f9f9f9 ivory\n- Text: #2d3435\n- Typography: NOTO_SERIF headlines + MANROPE body/UI\n- NO 1px borders — use background color shifts\n- 0px border radius — strict square\n- Glassmorphism: 80% opacity + 20px backdrop blur\n- Ambient shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(45,52,53,0.04)\n- Ghost borders: 15% opacity max\n- Interactions: 400ms ease-in-out\n- No icon-only buttons — always label + icon\n- Soft gold for promotions — NEVER sale red\n\n## Screens (MOBILE, one at a time):\n1. Home\n2. Collection/Category Listing\n3. Search\n4. Product Detail\n5. Wishlist\n6. Cart\n7. Checkout\n8. Sign In\n9. Sign Up\n10. Forgot Password\n11. Profile/Account\n12. Order History\n13. Order Detail\n14. Featured Collection Landing\n15. Editorial Campaign Page\n\n## Per-screen workflow:\n1. stitch__generate_screen_from_text (modelId: GEMINI_3_FLASH, deviceType: MOBILE)\n2. EXPECT timeout error → wait 50s → stitch__list_screens to verify\n3. If screen created → next screen\n4. If not → retry (max 3 attempts)\n\nReport final screen count when done.","label":"luxury-ecom:stitch-design-v3","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"stitch-design","thinking":"medium","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator","runTimeoutSeconds":900,"timeoutSeconds":10,"mode":"run","cleanup":"keep"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":159,"output":740,"cacheRead":80036,"cacheWrite":861,"totalTokens":81796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775974089590,"responseId":"062a69cbfc69e54bf5e56beac366d166"}}
