{"type":"message","id":"2effc6c2","parentId":"104eedc6","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:08:27.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. New agent spawned with the correct fire-and-forget + poll pattern. Let me update the user.","thinkingSignature":"e06424ec6d06680ffa85468f4de9a8b0ef8d4ca24e3cb8c373c2ea17d4ca74a3"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **`stitch-design` v3 — spawned với timeout logic đúng**\n\nPattern mới:\n- Gọi Stitch → timeout ~40s = **bình thường**\n- Đợi 50s\n- Poll `stitch__list_screens` kiểm tra\n- Nếu chưa có → retry (max 3 lần/screen)\n\nĐợi kết quả tự động."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":252,"output":123,"cacheRead":80274,"cacheWrite":1455,"totalTokens":82104,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775974102999,"responseId":"062a69d850b02e83e04291fcd81da11f"}}
