{"type":"message","id":"dbd13f13","parentId":"3e23d2f1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:25:56.112Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1065\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Maiychrus25 Company .Ltd id:-5212380728\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-12 06:25 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Maiychrus25 Company .Ltd\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nB"}],"timestamp":1775975156101}}
{"type":"message","id":"7037e585","parentId":"dbd13f13","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:26:15.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user chose option B - create a new Stitch project, apply the design system, and generate mobile screens. Let me create a new Stitch project first.","thinkingSignature":"e46872369d4c37ed805e5b29ed3f24888a92a837d9c8874805f24fd1c3266842"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w5ayg3xanm8s_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Create a new Stitch project and generate all 15 mobile screens for a luxury e-commerce app. \n\n## STEP 1: Create new project\nUse exec to call the Stitch MCP API to create a new project. Run this curl command:\n```\ncurl -X POST \"https://stitch.withgoogle.com/v1/projects\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat ~/.stitch-token 2>/dev/null || echo '')\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"displayName\": \"Aethelgard Noir - Luxury E-commerce\", \"projectType\": \"TEXT_TO_UI_PRO\"}'\n```\nIf that fails, try using the Stitch MCP tool directly. Report the new project ID.\n\n## STEP 2: Generate all 15 mobile screens (one at a time)\nFor each screen, follow this workflow:\n1. Call stitch__generate_screen_from_text with the screen prompt\n2. EXPECT timeout error (~40s) — this is NORMAL, not a failure\n3. Wait 60 seconds using: exec sleep 60\n4. Call stitch__list_screens on the new project to check if screen was created\n5. If screen exists → move to next screen\n6. If no screen → retry from step 1 (max 3 attempts per screen)\n\n## Design System: \"Aethelgard Noir\" (strict — follow exactly)\n- Primary: #5e5e5e charcoal\n- Secondary/Accent: #D4AF37 soft gold  \n- Surface: #f9f9f9 ivory\n- Text: #2d3435\n- Typography: NOTO_SERIF headlines + MANROPE body/UI\n- NO 1px borders — use background color shifts (surface-container tiers)\n- 0px border radius — strict square\n- Glassmorphism: 80% opacity + 20px backdrop blur for floating elements\n- Ambient shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(45,52,53,0.04)\n- Ghost borders: 15% opacity max\n- Interactions: 400ms ease-in-out\n- No icon-only buttons — always label + icon\n- Soft gold for promotions — NEVER sale red\n- No divider lines — use spacing (24px/32px gaps)\n\n## 15 Screens to generate (MOBILE):\n1. Home — cinematic hero, curated categories, editorial sections\n2. Collection/Category Listing — editorial product grid, minimal filters\n3. Search — premium zero-state, predictive suggestions\n4. Product Detail — gallery-first, luxury product storytelling\n5. Wishlist — curated personal closet feel\n6. Cart — premium review, clear totals\n7. Checkout — calm progression, one action per step\n8. Sign In — minimal, elegant, trustworthy\n9. Sign Up — same tone\n10. Forgot Password — minimal, refined\n11. Profile/Account — service-oriented dashboard\n12. Order History — clean list with status\n13. Order Detail — structured breakdown\n14. Featured Collection Landing — branded chapter page\n15. Editorial Campaign Page — immersive storytelling\n\nUse modelId: GEMINI_3_FLASH for generation. Report the new project ID and final screen count when complete.","label":"luxury-ecom:stitch-newproject","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"stitch-design","thinking":"medium","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator","runTimeoutSeconds":900,"timeoutSeconds":10,"mode":"run","cleanup":"keep"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":846,"cacheRead":76212,"cacheWrite":6431,"totalTokens":83489,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775975156113,"responseId":"062a6df6de2bec974164ee542b111398"}}
