agents\\n3. Current time: 07:03 UTC = 14:03 UTC+7 (2:03 PM). This is within the night silence window? Wait, night silence is 23:00-07:00 UTC+7. 14:03 UTC+7 = 07:03 UTC. So 07:03 UTC is right at the boundary - it's past 07:00 UTC+7 (midnight), so we're NOT in the night silence window. Actually, 23:00-07:00 UTC+7 = 16:00-00:00 UTC. \\n\\nSo 07:03 UTC falls outside the silence window. The 5-minute presence broadcast condition is met since the cron ran recently and there's 1 active session, so I should stay silent per the SESSIONS_ONLY mode instructions rather than sending a presence table.\\n\\nActually, wait—those two exec notifications about completed background processes aren't failures, they're just system notifications. The heartbeat itself is running fine with nothing critical happening. Since all conditions are normal and there's nothing requiring Khuowgn's attention, I'll reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"\\nHEARTBEAT_OK\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 149,\n            \"output\": 279,\n            \"totalTokens\": 55580,\n            \"cacheRead\": 5142,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 50010,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775977405742,\n          \"responseId\": \"062a76bf77fc6ab83097c3cbfe31dad3\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"9da4e3ca\",\n            \"seq\": 892\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\",\n      \"update