{"type":"message","id":"be8b078a","parentId":"bfd59631","timestamp":"2026-04-12T07:35:04.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the Confluence pages. There are HRM (Human Resource Management) related pages and OKRs pages. Let me get more pages and then read the most relevant ones for the CRM task.\n\nThe user wants a \"Company internal CRM\" which could relate to HRM pages. Let me read the most relevant pages - particularly the HRM-related ones since this is a company internal CRM.\n\nLet me get more pages first, then read the key ones.","thinkingSignature":"05a1ca5efe838e9594e674e732ca07b4ed06788aa83eb9895eb5bcfbd949982b"},{"type":"text","text":"Có 20 pages. Lấy thêm và đọc các page HRM — đây là core của CRM nội bộ.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mja1ui8nevbz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -u \"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com:ATATT3xFfGF0Xl6QZ-9lDBTiDym6FNGm1r6FJMt3u4ffIR8MjNDzl2oiKrRic_bdgOiIMWetDPY9FYMC_NPZ6O5uQVhiPip7oy2FlVGFqz5e214BGkaRoKmHz2XauaQG0A7rRq-7Lp8jp79Rdct2H61IouXCLFY4vQyXP9T9BPJT7ysxfnzJv7g=F3088272\" \\\n  \"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/space/AW/content/page?limit=50&start=20\" \\\n  -H \"Accept: application/json\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nresults=d.get('results',[])\nfor p in results:\n    title=p.get('title','')\n    pid=p.get('id','')\n    ver=p.get('version',{}).get('number','')\n    ancestors=[a.get('title','') for a in p.get('ancestors',[])]\n    print(f'  [{pid}] v{ver} | {\\\" > \\\".join(ancestors)} > {title}')\n\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":596,"output":458,"cacheRead":93319,"cacheWrite":1228,"totalTokens":95601,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775979295175,"responseId":"062a7e207a2bbca791f6d7acc9050738"}}
