{"type":"message","id":"1a3674ee","parentId":"c600347f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T07:36:00.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Confluence API is working now. I got detailed information about the \"Nhân viên\" (Employee) page. This contains functional specifications for an employee management module in the HRM system. Let me read more pages to build a comprehensive picture of what the AHV Works system includes.\n\nThe page shows detailed functional specs for:\n- Employee listing page with search/filter\n- Employee creation page with various fields (ID, name, phone, email, department, position, etc.)\n- Edit/Delete employee actions\n\nLet me read more pages to get a complete picture of all the modules.","thinkingSignature":"0024f2fb009f5419b787a8adb39daa47b1a10cd465eb6709161986b71a24587b"},{"type":"text","text":"Đọc được dữ liệu. Tiếp tục đọc các page quan trọng khác.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4kac9w67y4nf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"ATATT3xFfGF0Xl6QZ-9lDBTiDym6FNGm1r6FJMt3u4ffIR8MjNDzl2oiKrRic_bdgOiIMWetDPY9FYMC_NPZ6O5uQVhiPip7oy2FlVGFqz5e214BGkaRoKmHz2XauaQG0A7rRq-7Lp8jp79Rdct2H61IouXCLFY4vQyXP9T9BPJT7ysxfnzJv7g=F3088272\"\nUSER=\"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com\"\n\nfor PID in 94601218 95092740 95944796 96305161 99614745 96665627 96632896 104464406; do\n  echo \"===== PAGE $PID =====\"\n  curl -s -u \"$USER:$TOKEN\" \\\n    \"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/$PID?expand=body.storage,version,ancestors\" \\\n    -H \"Accept: application/json\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys,re,html\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\ntitle=d.get('title','')\nbody=d.get('body',{}).get('storage',{}).get('value','')\nver=d.get('version',{}).get('number','')\nancestors=' > '.join([a.get('title','') for a in d.get('ancestors',[])])\nbody=re.sub(r'<[^>]+>',' ',body)\nbody=re.sub(r'\\s+',' ',body).strip()\nbody=html.unescape(body)\nprint(f'[{PID}] v{ver} | {ancestors} > {title}')\nprint(body[:3500])\n\"\n  echo \"\"\ndone","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1456,"output":576,"cacheRead":96515,"cacheWrite":1335,"totalTokens":99882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775979347155,"responseId":"062a7e540008bf4d5967672586d9658d"}}
