{"type":"message","id":"39ff619a","parentId":"6df832ff","timestamp":"2026-04-12T07:37:12.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - curl still works. There seems to be a rate limiting issue with urllib. Let me continue fetching the remaining pages using curl. I have enough data from the first two pages to understand the pattern. Let me quickly read a few more key pages to understand the full scope.\n\nActually, I now have a good understanding of the system. This is clearly an **HRM (Human Resource Management) system** for AHV, containing:\n1. **Nhân viên** (Employee) - Employee management with ID, name, email, phone, address, avatar, department, position, status, created date\n2. **Tài khoản** (Account) - Account/user management for the system\n\n\n3. **Chấm công** (Time tracking) - Timekeeping management\n4. **Ca làm việc** (Work shifts) - Shift management\n5. **Loại ca làm việc** (Shift types)\n6. **Loại thu nhập** (Income types)\n7. **Chức vụ** (Positions) - Job titles/positions\n8. **Phòng ban** (Departments)\n9. **Loại nghỉ phép** (Leave types)\n10. **Lịch trình** (Schedules)\n11. **Bảng xếp hạng giờ làm** (Work hour ranking)\n12. **OKRs** - Objectives and Key Results\n13. **Phân quyền** (Permissions)\n14. **Lịch sử làm việc** (Work history)\n15. **Tạo lịch check-in** (Create check-in schedule)\n16. **Quản lí nghỉ phép** (Leave management)\n17. **Điểm đánh giá** (Evaluation scores)\n18. **Chi tiết bảng đánh giá OKRs** (OKR evaluation details)\n19. **Bảng xếp hạng** (Rankings)\n\nThe system appears to be a comprehensive HR platform with modules spanning employee management, payroll, scheduling, performance tracking, and organizational hierarchy.\n\nThe user described this as a \"Company internal CRM,\" but looking at the Confluence specs, this is really an **HRM system** (Human Resource Management) — a web application handling employee records, time tracking, shift management, leave requests, OKRs, and performance evaluations. I'm noticing some inconsistency though: the ahv-qlhv project I have in my MEMORY.md is about teacher driving training, which is different from what I'm seeing in the HRM specs, so there might be multiple projects or the user is mixing things up.\n\nThe user probably wants me to build the AHV Works HRM system described in Confluence, so I should pull the remaining key pages like Phòng ban, Ca làm việc, and Quản lý chấm công to get the full picture, then summarize what I'm building based on the 28 pages available. Looking at the Confluence specs more carefully, the user specifically mentioned \"Company internal CRM\" — that's HRM (Human Resource Management). The modules cover employee management, accounts, time tracking, shifts, leave, departments, positions, OKRs, permissions, work history, check-ins, and rankings. I have enough context to understand the system scope, so I should move forward with building it. I'm going to check the remaining key pages to confirm the complete scope, then move forward with planning the implementation.","thinkingSignature":"c8307fc7aadecf379c0459baed776458b74e0a4c3eb6872efaa83644752ad5e0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iiopgalwo9y6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"ATATT3xFfGF0Xl6QZ-9lDBTiDym6FNGm1r6FJMt3u4ffIR8MjNDzl2oiKrRic_bdgOiIMWetDPY9FYMC_NPZ6O5uQVhiPip7oy2FlVGFqz5e214BGkaRoKmHz2XauaQG0A7rRq-7Lp8jp79Rdct2H61IouXCLFY4vQyXP9T9BPJT7ysxfnzJv7g=F3088272\"\nUSER=\"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com\"\n\nfor PID in 95944796 99614745 96632896 95387652 96665627 104726536 104726545 99582025 125403137; do\n  echo \"== $PID ==\"\n  curl -s -u \"$USER:$TOKEN\" \\\n    \"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/$PID?expand=body.storage,version\" \\\n    -H \"Accept: application/json\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys,re,html\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nt=d.get('title','')\nb=d.get('body',{}).get('storage',{}).get('value','')\nver=d.get('version',{}).get('number','')\nb=re.sub(r'<[^>]+>',' ',b)\nb=re.sub(r'\\s+',' ',b).strip()\nb=html.unescape(b)\nprint(f'[{ver}] {t}')\nprint(b[:3000])\n\"\n  echo \"\"\n  sleep 1\ndone","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2419,"output":1132,"cacheRead":100960,"cacheWrite":782,"totalTokens":105293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775979397343,"responseId":"062a7e86d8fbf2f484a1b1b3f9e970a8"}}
