{"type":"message","id":"bc5c27d6","parentId":"59635374","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:11:29.273Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture of the codebase:\n\n**Backend (AHV HRM Backend)**:\n- Express + TypeScript\n- MongoDB (mongoose)\n- Socket.IO (real-time)\n- Redis (ioredis)\n- JWT auth\n- node-cron (scheduled tasks)\n- Joi (validation)\n- Swagger\n- winston logging\n- bcrypt (password hashing)\n\n**Frontend (HRM UI)**:\n- React + TypeScript\n- Vite\n- Ant Design (antd)\n- Redux Toolkit\n- Tiptap (rich text editor)\n- Socket.IO client\n- React Router\n- Axios\n- Sass\n\n\n- \nNow I'm diving into the module structure to understand what each one does and how they interact.","thinkingSignature":"10f65110e7013f8df21ef472ac672643224a41616e76d40969c15887ef163f67"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kfonhztit8zi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65\"\nBE_ID=78077025\n\n# Backend modules\ncurl -s --header \"PRIVATE-TOKEN: $TOKEN\" \\\n  \"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/$BE_ID/repository/tree?path=src/modules&per_page=100\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nitems=json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor i in sorted(items, key=lambda x: x.get('path','')):\n    t=i.get('type','')\n    p=i.get('path','').replace('src/modules/','')\n    print(('  ' if t=='tree' else '  [f] ')+p)\n\"\n\necho \"\"\n# Backend swagger summary\ncurl -s --header \"PRIVATE-TOKEN: $TOKEN\" \\\n  \"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/$BE_ID/repository/files/swagger.yaml/raw\" | python3 -c \"\nimport yaml,sys\nd=yaml.safe_load(sys.stdin)\npaths=d.get('paths',{})\nprint(f'Total endpoints: {len(paths)}')\nfor p in sorted(paths.keys())[:40]:\n    methods=list(paths[p].keys())\n    print(f'  {p} [{\\\" \\\".join(methods)}]')\n\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"swagger parse error\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":479,"