{"type":"message","id":"93506d3f","parentId":"304805ce","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:11:39.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! Now I have a comprehensive view of the AHV Works source code. Let me read a few more key files - the frontend modules structure and some key components.\n\nKey findings:\n- **Backend**: Express + TypeScript + MongoDB, 38 modules, 55+ endpoints\n- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript + Ant Design + Vite\n\nLet me now provide a comprehensive summary to the user about the AHV Works source code that was found.","thinkingSignature":"0b51b237640be980ec3f7036e06412d482c07e7afdaadb8994e91a17adbc8b35"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eqfrsgmas6em_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65\"\nFE_ID=78077037\n\n# Frontend modules\ncurl -s --header \"PRIVATE-TOKEN: $TOKEN\" \\\n  \"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/$FE_ID/repository/tree?path=src/modules&per_page=100\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nitems=json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor i in sorted(items, key=lambda x: x.get('path','')):\n    t=i.get('type','')\n    p=i.get('path','').replace('src/modules/','')\n    print(('  ' if t=='tree' else '  [f] ')+p)\n\"\n\necho \"\"\n# Read README for context\ncurl -s --header \"PRIVATE-TOKEN: $TOKEN\" \\\n  \"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/$FE_ID/repository/files/README.md/raw\" | head -50","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":666,"output":348,"cacheRead":114526,"cacheWrite":1493,"totalTokens":117033,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775981491244,"responseId":"062a86b49f8a14288df2084cd8ced9d6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"06383fce","parentId":"93506d3f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:11:41.084Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_eqfrsgmas6em_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"account\n  attendance\n  auth\n  checkins\n  contracts\n  dashboard\n  departments\n  employees\n  leave-requests\n  logs\n  niko-emotions\n  notifications\n  okrs\n  payrolls\n  positions\n  schedules\n  settings\n  shifts\n\nUI for hrm"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1472,"aggregated":"account\n  attendance\n  auth\n  checkins\n  contracts\n  dashboard\n  departments\n  employees\n  leave-requests\n  logs\n  niko-emotions\n  notifications\n  okrs\n  payrolls\n  positions\n  schedules\n  settings\n  shifts\n\nUI for hrm","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775981501063}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed0bb9f0","parentId":"06383fce","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:11:55.831Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me summarize this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"4f0e33f2627b56d796781188adc1716d1c4782ad5f53c78ed43e58d65e73314d"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] ✅ **GitLab connected — AHV Works source đọc xong**\n\n---\n\n## 🏗️ AHV Works — Source Code Overview\n\n### Backend (`ahv-works/ahv-hrm/ahv-hrm-backend`)\n- **Stack:** Express + TypeScript + MongoDB (mongoose) + Socket.IO + Redis + JWT\n- **38 modules** | **55+ API endpoints**\n\n| Module | Mô tả |\n|--------|--------|\n| `accounts` | Quản lý tài khoản |\n| `employees` | Quản lý nhân viên |\n| `departments` | Phòng ban |\n| `positions` | Chức vụ |\n| `roles` / `permissions` | Phân quyền |\n| `attendances` | Chấm công |\n| `shifts` / `shiftTypes` | Ca làm việc |\n| `leaveRequests` / `leaveTypes` | Nghỉ phép |\n| `leaveBalances` | Tích lũy phép |\n| `checkins` | Check-in GPS |\n| `okrs` / `objectives` / `keyResults` | OKRs |\n| `payrolls` / `payrollDetails` | Lương thưởng |\n| `contracts` | Hợp đồng |\n| `deductions` / `incomeTypes` | Khấu trừ/thu nhập |\n| `nikoEmotions` / `nikoGifts` / `nikoWallets` | Khen thưởng sao + đổi quà |\n| `nikoCriteria` / `nikoSectors` | Tiêu chí khen |\n| `notifications` | Thông báo |\n| `systemLogs` | Nhật ký hệ thống |\n| `globalSettings` | Cấu hình |\n\n### Frontend (`ahv-works/ahv-hrm/ahv-hrm-frontend`)\n- **Stack:** React + TypeScript + Vite + Ant Design + Redux Toolkit + Socket.IO\n- **18 modules**\n\n| Module | UI screens |\n|--------|-----------|\n| `dashboard` | Bảng điều khiển |\n| `employees` | Quản lý nhân viên |\n| `departments` | Phòng ban |\n| `positions` | Chức vụ |\n| `attendance` | Chấm công |\n| `shifts` | Ca làm việc |\n| `leave-requests` | Đơn nghỉ phép |\n| `checkins` | Check-in |\n| `okrs` | OKRs |\n| `payrolls` | Lương thưởng |\n| `contracts` | Hợp đồng |\n| `niko-emotions` | Khen thưởng |\n| `notifications` | Thông báo |\n| `settings` | Cài đặt |\n| `account` | Tài khoản |\n| `auth` | Đăng nhập |\n\n---\n\n## 📌 Bước tiếp theo\n\nHệ thống **đã tồn tại đầy đủ** ở trên GitLab. Cần xác định:\n\n**Bạn muốn làm gì với AHV Works?**\n- **A)** Review code hiện tại (audit chất lượng, bảo mật, performance)\n- **B)** Thêm tính năng mới (Chat, Bảng xếp hạng, Khen thưởng nâng cao)\n- **C)** Tái cấu trúc / refactor module nào đó\n- **D)** Deploy & vận hành hệ thống hiện tại"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":166,"output":870,"cacheRead":115525,"cacheWrite":1423,"totalTokens":117984,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775981501098,"responseId":"062a86befbf4218789f873f419560cc7"}}
