{"type":"message","id":"7a90c888","parentId":"9de923af","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:13:16.037Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1193\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Maiychrus25 Company .Ltd id:-5212380728\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-12 08:12 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Maiychrus25 Company .Ltd\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nnếu giờ tôi bảo bạn review code thì bạn làm gì"}],"timestamp":1775981596009}}
{"type":"message","id":"b714d597","parentId":"7a90c888","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:13:31.715Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what I would do if they asked me to review the code. Let me explain the orchestration pipeline for a code review task.","thinkingSignature":"29eb95cce8975acd73f2eb2f5145c2e22dcb847701437e73e357113bfadacbde"},{"type":"text","text":"Dạ, nếu bạn bảo **\"review code\"**, đây là pipeline orchestration của mình:\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Code Review Pipeline\n\n**Bước 1 — Xác định scope review**\n\nBạn muốn review toàn bộ hay chỉ module nào?\n- Toàn bộ backend (38 modules, 55 endpoints)\n- Backend module cụ thể (VD: `attendances`, `okrs`, `checkins`)\n- Frontend (18 modules)\n- Cả hai\n\n**Bước 2 — Spawn agents review song song**\n\n| Agent | Phụ trách |\n|-------|-----------|\n| `senior-backend` | API structure, 3-layer arch (controller → service → repo), security, validation |\n| `code-reviewer` | Code quality, patterns, DRY/KISS, error handling |\n| `typescript-reviewer` | Type safety, TypeScript correctness |\n| `security-reviewer` | Auth, permissions, OWASP, input validation |\n| `database-reviewer` | MongoDB schemas, indexes, queries |\n| `performance-optimizer` | N+1 queries, slow endpoints, memory leaks |\n| `senior-qa` | Test coverage, edge cases |\n\n**Bước 3 — Mỗi agent viết báo cáo vào file riêng**\n\n```\n/master-orchestrator/\n  reviews/\n    backend-review.md\n    frontend-review.md\n    security-review.md\n    database-review.md\n    performance-review.md\n    summary-review.md\n```\n\n**Bước 4 — Mình tổng hợp → gửi bạn `RELEASE.md`**\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ Ví dụ nhanh\n\nNếu bạn nói **\"review module checkins\"**:\n\n```\n1. senior-backend đọc src/modules/checkins/*\n2. security-reviewer kiểm tra GPS logic, permission\n3. code-reviewer kiểm tra code quality\n4. database-reviewer kiểm tra schema + indexes\n5. Mình tổng hợp → báo cáo chi tiết + điểm cần fix\n```\n\n---\n\n## ❓ Cần bạn trả lời\n\n**Bạn muốn review scope nào?**\n- **Toàn bộ** backend + frontend\n- **Module cụ thể** — chỉ rõ module name\n- **1 file/số files cụ thể** — gửi path hoặc paste code\n\nChọn và mình bắt đầu ngay."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":603,"cacheRead":116183,"cacheWrite":1304,"totalTokens":118090,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775981596071,"responseId":"062a871d32973dd7af6fb2e201b31ac5"}}
