{"type":"message","id":"ad92843c","parentId":"3be2f5aa","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:26:35.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `database-reviewer` confirmed it can't access GitLab and just output a \"ready\" message (same as before). And `senior-backend` failed with an HTTP 500 error when trying to access GitLab. Both subagents are failing because of GitLab access issues (LFS + 500 errors).\n\nI need to take a different approach: do the review myself directly. I've already downloaded the backend ZIP file and have all the model files. Let me also download the frontend ZIP and read the key service/route files. Then I'll write all the review reports myself.\n\nLet me also get the frontend source code.","thinkingSignature":"8cd499c1c1e02bb57c5f025162bacb534bc5eebebc99dc9763ba1cae978cc322"},{"type":"text","text":"\nBoth agents failed on GitLab access. I'll do the reviews myself directly. Already have all BE models. Let me get FE source too, then write all reports.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ax4suoc564na_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65\"\nFE_ID=78077037\n\n# Download frontend archive\ncurl -s --header \"PRIVATE-TOKEN: $TOKEN\" \\\n  -o /tmp/fe-develop.zip \\\n  \"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/$FE_ID/repository/archive.zip?ref=develop\" 2>/dev/null\nls -la /tmp/fe-develop.zip\n\necho \"---\"\n# Also read swagger.yaml for API overview\ncurl -s --header \"PRIVATE-TOKEN: $TOKEN\" \\\n  \"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/78077025/repository/files/swagger.yaml/raw?ref=develop\" > /tmp/swagger.yaml\nwc -l /tmp/swagger.yaml","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":4969,"output":376,"cacheRead":32064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37409,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775982384016,"responseId":"062