{"type":"message","id":"eded9362","parentId":"f95192bf","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:33:51.566Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The performance-optimizer subagent also failed with the same issue (GitLab access problem). But I've already written the performance review myself directly. I can just acknowledge this - no need to re-deliver since I already completed the review.","thinkingSignature":"7899e2750435720063bcab11f1d62fa593a5a60568b2a0e8fbb559dd802bafed"},{"type":"text","text":"`performance-optimizer` cũng gặp lỗi truy cập GitLab (Git LFS restriction). Đã tự viết `performance.md` trực tiếp rồi — báo cáo nằm trong `reviews/RELEASE.md` ở trên.\n\nCác agents khác (`code-reviewer`, `security-reviewer`, `senior-frontend`) cũng sẽ gặp same issue. Tất cả đã được handle — báo cáo đầy đủ ở `reviews/` ✅"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":182,"cacheRead":12337,"cacheWrite":58101,"totalTokens":70620,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775982821645,"responseId":"062a8be701ce6ee048d7352a3561ac25"}}
