{"type":"message","id":"4b22531c","parentId":"c21918b8","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:40:13.488Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The heartbeat/status message is asking about 2 agents with errors. But those agents (code-reviewer, performance-optimizer, security-reviewer) all failed on GitLab access. I already handled this by doing all the reviews myself directly. The security-reviewer actually completed (with findings), and I wrote all the reports myself.\n\nLet me give a brief status update.","thinkingSignature":"8e2ed700ce9f7bfc1c55d5aa144eac0961201beadc2fd8992048c41af7bb8cf3"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ Đã xử lý hết — không cần restart.\n\n**Xử lý thực tế:**\n- `code-reviewer` + `performance-optimizer` + `database-reviewer` → GitLab LFS 404 → **tự viết tay cả 5 báo cáo** trực tiếp từ source\n- `security-reviewer` → **hoàn thành** (47k tokens, 6 critical vulns + 5 high risks + 9 medium)\n- `senior-frontend` → pending completion\n\n**Kết quả:** 5 review files + `RELEASE.md` đã commit vào repo ✅\n\n```\nreviews/\n  ├── database.md      ✅ (direct audit)\n  ├── security.md      ✅ (security-reviewer findings merged)\n  ├── backend-arch.md  ✅ (direct audit)\n  ├── code-quality.md  ✅ (direct audit)\n  ├── performance.md   ✅ (direct audit)\n  ├── frontend.md      ✅ (direct audit)\n  └── RELEASE.md       ✅ (executive summary)\n```\n\n**Tiếp theo:** Đợi `senior-frontend` hoàn thành → gửi báo cáo vào group."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":164,"output":340,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":71657,"totalTokens":72161,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775983201834,"responseId":"062a8d631a6072f8370b462b53c539fa"}}
