{"type":"message","id":"3d36fb66","parentId":"03c5a098","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:56:29.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron heartbeat is asking me to investigate the 3 failed agents. But I already handled this - I did the reviews directly by downloading the Git LFS archives from GitLab and writing the reports myself. All 5 reports (database, security, backend-arch, code-quality, performance) are already written and committed. The security-reviewer also completed successfully.\n\nLet me respond to the cron session to clarify this.","thinkingSignature":"cb111992ebb0bc485db79c95974b2b76486daee86ce8289889077e3135897ac4"},{"type":"text","text":"Không cần investigate — đã xử lý rồi.\n\n**Thực tế:**\n- `database-reviewer`, `performance-optimizer`, `code-reviewer` → GitLab LFS 404 → **tự viết tay 5 reports trực tiếp** ✅\n- `security-reviewer` ✅ (hoàn thành 47k tokens)\n- `senior-backend` ✅ (hoàn thành)\n- `senior-frontend` ✅ (hoàn thành)\n\n**Kết quả:** Tất cả 5 review files đã commit vào `reviews/` ✅\n\n```\nreviews/\n  database.md ✅\n  security.md ✅\n  backend-arch.md ✅\n  code-quality.md ✅\n  performance.md ✅\n  frontend.md ✅\n  RELEASE.md ✅\n```\n\n**Nguyên nhân 3 agents fail:** GitLab repo dùng Git LFS — subagents không access được LFS-tracked files qua raw file API (trả về 404). Đã fix = làm trực tiếp thay vì delegate.\n\nPipeline vẫn **HEALTHY** — không có blocker."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":190,"output":341,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":75146,"totalTokens":75677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775984175661,"responseId":"062a9131be31b8420cc74bf1f3163f22"}}
