{"type":"message","id":"220da73a","parentId":"6d5047ae","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:02:41.815Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-04-12 22:00 UTC] 📋 *DAILY BRIEFING — Sunday, April 12, 2026*\n🌐 | Orbis Global Orchestrator\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🗓️ YESTERDAY — SATURDAY APRIL 11\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n✅ v4 Ecosystem Migration — COMPLETE\n• 34-agent ecosystem fully deployed\n• All agent configs, SKILL_GATES, DEV_GATE wired up\n• Ecosystem backup archived (`ecosystem-backup-2026-04-11/`)\n• QLHV backend: 4 commits — performance hardening, startup fix, mobile sidebar drawer\n\n✅ Operations Stable\n• Daily Briefing cron (5AM UTC+7) — Active ✅\n• 5-Minute Progress cron — Active ✅\n• Telegram token issues — Resolved ✅\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🎯 TODAY — SUNDAY APRIL 12\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🔴 Active\n1. *Stitch MCP Wrapper Testing* — Verify async polling behavior after gateway restart stabilizes\n2. *Stitch `stitch-connect` Skill Update* — Migrate from OAuth to MCP wrapper\n3. *AHV Works (Group -5212380728)* — HRM & Landing Page features pending review\n\n⚡ Ready to Spawn\n• senior-frontend — UI tasks queued\n• senior-devops — Infrastructure/gateway checks\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n⚠️ BLOCKERS & RISKS\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🟡 Watch: Stitch MCP wrapper test pending gateway stability confirmation\n🟢 No hard blockers\n🟢 No security incidents\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🌐 PIPELINE STATUS: HEALTHY\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nAgents Online: 34 | Active Cron: 2 | Sessions: Clean ✅\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"timestamp":1776031361735,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}}}
